thread.title: Sarah Wineland
thread.title_full: 42nd Street Photo reviewed by Sarah Wineland

author: Sarah Wineland
title: Sarah Wineland
text: I order a lens that wasn't the right fit for my camera and had no idea. Luckily, 42nd Street called me prior to shipping and advised me on which comparable lens I should purchase. They patiently explained the difference between the two and helped me figure out what was the best option. Highly recommend!
